2. cs.RO (Robotics): The challenge involves building a controller for a musculoskeletal model, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence techniques such as reinforcement learning, imitation learning, and policy blending. 
4. cs.CV (Computer Vision): Although not the main focus, some participants used computer vision techniques to preprocess the input data. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of control theory and expert knowledge to improve the performance of the controllers.
